              "free_text": [
                " The errors in the cross sections are",
                "estimated As 12 %.",
                "In many cases cross sections were measured in",
                "duplicate.  The results usually agreed within 5%.",
                "Regarding a given excitation function the cross",
                "sections have a relative error of 5% with respect to",
                "each other. The energy values below 16 MeV can have an",
                "error of about 1 MeV."
              ]
